I"X<p>The Griffith Lab is located at the The McDonnell Genome Institute at Washington University in St Louis. The McDonnell Genome Institute is one of four large-scale sequencing centers in the United States funded by the National Institutes of Health (NIH) and National Human Genome Research Institute (NHGRI).</p>

<p>In addition to support from Washington University, the Griffith Lab has received support from the following external funding agencies, non-profit foundations, and other organizations.</p>

